entries.arrival_phase_1: Getting a lock on the rebel command group. None of them is to make it out alive.
entries.arrival_phase_2: We have the lock. Sending that information to your nav computer. It looks like they are trying to make a run for it.
entries.assassinate_success: The rebels will remember this day. You have done very well. Report your success back to your superior.
entries.destroy_escort: There are still some other rebel ships in the area. Make sure none of them escape.
entries.escort_remaining: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:pcontrast3 <%DI enemy escorts remaining.>
entries.escort_wiped_out: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:pcontrast3 <Enemy escort fighters destroyed.>
entries.failed_escape: You let them slip through your fingers. Report this failure to your superior immediately.
entries.quest_escort_d: Make sure no one gets out alive. Destroy the escorts. Once completed return to your commander.
entries.quest_location_d: Remain in the Dantooine system and intercept the Rebel command vessel.
entries.quest_target_d: Intercept and destroy the Rebel command vessel inside the Dantooine system.
entries.title: Dantooine System: Destroy the Rebel Command Vessel
entries.title_d: Destroy the Rebel command vessel in the Dantooine system. It was on its way to pick up the captured shuttles that appeared in the system. Show the Rebels that their actions will not go unpunished.
